### BoTCoin API — Phase 10 acceptance smoke tests
### REST Client for VS Code — run requests top to bottom.
### The @job_id variable is captured automatically from the optimizer submit response.

@host = http://localhost:8000
@token = your-api-token-here

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# BACKTEST
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [BT-1] Basic backtest — no fee, full history, recompute path
POST {{host}}/backtest
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR",
  "fee_pct": 0.0
}

###

### [BT-2] Backtest with fee — checks fee_abs + pnl_abs in operations
POST {{host}}/backtest
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR",
  "fee_pct": 0.4
}

###

### [BT-3] Backtest using live calibration cache (use_live_config=true)
### Requires the scheduler to have run calculate_trading_parameters at least once.
### If the cache is cold, falls through to "recompute" — result is identical data.
POST {{host}}/backtest
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR",
  "fee_pct": 0,
  "use_live_config": true
}

###

### [BT-4] Date-sliced backtest — forces the "slice" + recompute path
POST {{host}}/backtest
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR",
  "fee_pct": 0.4,
  "start": "2026-05-20",
  "end": "2026-06-01"
}

###

### [BT-5] Backtest capped at 10 operations
POST {{host}}/backtest
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR",
  "fee_pct": 0.4,
  "max_ops": 10
}

###

### [BT-6] ETHEUR pair
POST {{host}}/backtest
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "ETHEUR",
  "fee_pct": 0.4
}

###

### [BT-7] Unknown pair → 400
POST {{host}}/backtest
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "DOGEEUR"
}

###

### [BT-8] No auth → 401 (or 403 depending on middleware)
POST {{host}}/backtest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR"
}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OPTIMIZER — submit
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [OPT-1] Submit optimizer job — OPTIMIZE mode, low n_trials for quick smoke
# @name submitJob
POST {{host}}/optimizer/jobs
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR",
  "mode": "OPTIMIZE",
  "fee_pct": 0.4,
  "split_method": "BOTH",
  "train_split": 0.8,
  "n_trials": 300,
  "seed": 42
}

###

@job_id = {{submitJob.response.body.job_id}}

### [OPT-2] Poll job status (run repeatedly until status != "running")
GET {{host}}/optimizer/jobs/{{job_id}}
X-Api-Token: {{token}}

###

### [OPT-3] Submit while [OPT-1] is still running → 409 Conflict
POST {{host}}/optimizer/jobs
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR",
  "mode": "CURRENT",
  "split_method": "RESET",
  "n_trials": 1
}

###

### [OPT-4] List all jobs (default limit=20)
GET {{host}}/optimizer/jobs
X-Api-Token: {{token}}

###

### [OPT-5] List with explicit limit
GET {{host}}/optimizer/jobs?limit=5
X-Api-Token: {{token}}

###

### [OPT-6] Get unknown job → 404
GET {{host}}/optimizer/jobs/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
X-Api-Token: {{token}}

###

### [OPT-7] OPTIMIZE mode, RESET split
POST {{host}}/optimizer/jobs
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR",
  "mode": "OPTIMIZE",
  "fee_pct": 0.4,
  "split_method": "RESET",
  "train_split": 0.8,
  "n_trials": 30,
  "seed": 7
}

###

### [OPT-8] CURRENT mode — evaluates the live .env config, returns 1 trial
POST {{host}}/optimizer/jobs
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR",
  "mode": "CURRENT",
  "fee_pct": 0.4,
  "split_method": "RESET"
}

###

### [OPT-9] Unknown pair → 400
POST {{host}}/optimizer/jobs
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "DOGEEUR",
  "mode": "OPTIMIZE",
  "n_trials": 10
}

###

### [OPT-10] n_trials out of range → 422 Unprocessable Entity
POST {{host}}/optimizer/jobs
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR",
  "mode": "AGGRESSIVE",
  "n_trials": 0
}

###

### [OPT-11] Invalid mode → 422
POST {{host}}/optimizer/jobs
X-Api-Token: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pair": "XBTEUR",
  "mode": "BADMODE",
  "n_trials": 10
}

###

