GET {{host}}/status
X-Api-Token: {{token}}

###

### [REG-2] Market data
GET {{host}}/market
X-Api-Token: {{token}}

###

### [REG-3] Positions
GET {{host}}/positions
X-Api-Token: {{token}}

###

### [REG-4] Balance
GET {{host}}/balance
X-Api-Token: {{token}}

